@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_osgyeh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.30)) / (0.13 - 0.48))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin(v1))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.92 / v0 + 0.90)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(v0) * ((v2 + 0.34 + tmp + 0.57) - (v1 + 0.05 + tmp + 0.25)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.08)) * ((v2 + 0.92 + v1 + 0.98) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
